narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes take this course by all means. I have nothing bad to say about it.
Yes i would recommend this course to another student, it was great.

I would definately recommend this class if you're interested in understanding management schemes as they relate to the environment and the complexities thereof. Professor Fotos does a great job facilitating conversation and guiding you on your final paper.

Yes definitely. Be wary it less about "democracy" versus "authoritarian" methods of dealing with environmental issues, but more of a look at institutional design principles. Prof Fotos is great just make sure you do the readings to avoid his wrath.
